Gratuitous Arguments by Walker:

This has caused to confusion or harm to anyone, and is
unlikely to do so in the future. I have already terminated the pledge
regarding "e" and started using "C-walker" again in my signature,
which I will continue to do until I think of a new nickname. It is
also likely that if I get the 3 rests for this I won't be able to pay
them off for at least a month, even under the new cards system.

